task.summary: Added bcrypt and password authentication to the developers model. In addition, the password now requires confirmation, and is stored as a hash instead of a raw text password.
User and password login now work correctly. On succesful login, the page is directed to the user.show html file. On a fial, an alert is displayed saying that the email/password was incorrect.

Sessions now fully working correctly. Admin and Developer user types working correctly. Forces a login, and users can only be created by admins. This commit has the sections where logins are required not commented.
List the developers that are asisgned to the project under project show. Also, add project to user.
Hide fields of users based on if a user is an admin or a developer, such as creating, toggling developer and admin, etc.
Search function in the stories section, though it only searches by Title for now. It needs a precise match.
Added storyboard to the projects page.
Developers can now sign up for stories within the story index page. Todo: make sure the developer is part of the project they are signing up for.
Developers can now sign up for stories within the story index page. Todo: make sure the developer is part of the project they are signing up for.
Stories now correctly select and save point values and stages.
Small change to just emit developer fields from edit and new stories.
